title: El Tiante
itunes:title: El Tiante
description: Former Red Sox legend Louie Tiant, and Mike Bellody, from El Tiante  Cigars join The Cigar Authority to talk about their brand new releases:  the Habano Rosado Natural, and the Habano Oscuro Maduro. Later in the  show Fred Smith from "SmithFest" makes an appearance to talk about his  world records and upcoming events.
